        <p data-role="text">Today is World Alzheimer&#x2019;s Day, and de&#xAD;men&#xAD;tia is no bar&#xAD;rier to stay&#xAD;ing ac&#xAD;tive, as Madam See Liang Hau, 85, shows. She teaches oth&#xAD;ers how to cook via&#xD;&#xA;Face&#xAD;book Live in a se&#xAD;ries by her home, Apex Har&#xAD;mony Lodge, to em&#xAD;power res&#xAD;i&#xAD;dents like her. As Covid-19 sees many go on&#xAD;line to learn and com&#xAD;mu&#xAD;ni&#xAD;cate, The Straits Times cap&#xAD;tures some of their ex&#xAD;pe&#xAD;ri&#xAD;ences.</p>
